g">Đăng cao khâu nhi vọng viễn hải - 登高丘而望遠海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/Ngu-m%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n-Ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-HZRGAdGrdacRS5IreskrXA">Ngu mỹ nhân - Chẩm thượng - 虞美人—枕上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/author-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%B1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-lai-ng%C3%B4n-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-s%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-CFGlXtKzg-7M-QcXEABMCw">Nhân tự Bắc Ninh lai, ngôn Bắc Ninh sự cảm tác - 人自北寧來言北寧事感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-h%E1%BB%93ng-mai-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-fbLb4cV5a4OAJeETdqz1KQ">Phú đắc hồng mai hoa kỳ 2 - 賦得紅梅花其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%95-ch%C6%B0-tri%E1%BA%BFt-nh%C3%A2n/poem-AcafTrS8O_a9zrO1myLsZg">Tự cổ chư triết nhân - 自古諸哲人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Y%E1%BA%BFn-T%E1%BB%AD-l%C3%A2u-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-kqHIpP0t2iYehbALpjtbXA">Yến Tử lâu kỳ 3 - 燕子樓其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
